<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_SP49_CrystalCreations_WearingGiftingJewelry" s="360184">
  <T n="name">0x68922460<!--Wearing & Gifting Jewelry--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_WearingGiftingJewelry_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:ffa9d5d983ec20cb</T>
      <T n="text">0xC7A3D740<!--To have your Sim wear crafted Jewelry, select either <b><font color='#199C2C'>Wear with Current Outfit</font></b> or <b><font color='#199C2C'>Wear with All Outfits</font></b> under the Wear category on the Jewelry item. Now your Sim will wear the piece with the selected outfit(s) until they remove it from one or all outfits.\n\nThis will <b><font color='#199C2C'>replace</font></b> any Jewelry in the same slot. Sims may wear several rings or bracelets, as long as they're on different wrists or fingers!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_WearingGiftingJewelry_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:ffa9d5d983ec20c8</T>
      <T n="text">0xBDC004D3<!--If the Jewelry piece is in the world, your Sim will pick it up and add it to their <b><font color='#199C2C'>inventory</font></b> first. Wearable Jewelry will have a special <b><font color='#199C2C'>icon</font></b> on it, which turns green when the piece is worn with any outfit.\n\nOnce your Sim has put on crafted Jewelry in Live Mode, you can take it off and put it on again in <b><font color='#199C2C'>Create a Sim</font></b>.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_WearingGiftingJewelry_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:ffa9d5d983ec20c9</T>
      <T n="text">0x9B3C07D9<!--Your Sim can <b><font color='#199C2C'>gift</font></b> crafted Jewelry to other Sims!\n\nPut the Jewelry in your Sim's inventory, and select the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Gift to</font></b> interaction on the Jewelry piece. You can also use the interaction <b><font color='#199C2C'>Gift Jewelry</font></b> on other Sims in the Friendly social pie menu, then Affection.\n\nThe Sim receiving the gift will wear their new Jewelry with their <b><font color='#199C2C'>current outfit</font></b>.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InSP49\UI\Tutorial\CrystalCreations_WearingGiftingJewelry_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:ffa9d5d983ec20ce</T>
      <T n="text">0xF0056812<!--Sims can use a crafted Ring to <b><font color='#199C2C'>propose</font></b> to their Partner!\n\nPut it in their inventory and use the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Propose to</font></b> interaction on the Ring, or the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Propose with Crafted Ring</font></b> interaction on their partner in the Romance category.\n\nThe Sim who gets proposed to will wear their new Ring with <b><font color='#199C2C'>all outfits</font></b>.--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
  <L n="tags">
    <E>Lesson_SP49_CrystalCreations</E>
  </L>
</I>